title: Ducting
long_description:
Constructed of a heavy duty 3-ply, aluminum foil laminate, this product comes conveniently boxed in 25 ft lengths, compressed. Ducting offers only slightly higher air flow resistance than rigid straight duct.

We also have stainless steel hose clamps which are perfect for any air cooled reflectors, or carbon filters.
